 

Carolina Power  Light Company, Docket No. 50261, H. B. Robinson Steam 
Electric Plant, Unit No. 2, Darlington County, South Carolina 





Date of application for amendment:

 October 14, 1993. 



Brief description of amendment:

 The amendment revises TS 4.2.2 to remove the schedule for withdrawal of reactor vessel material surveillance specimens.




Date of issuance:

 September 6, 1994. 



Effective date:

 September 6, 1994. 



Amendment No. 150. 

Facility Operating License No. DPR23. 

Amendment revises the Technical Specifications. 



Date of initial notice in 

Federal Register

: November 10, 1993 (58 FR 59745). The Commission's related evaluation of the amendment is contained in a Safety Evaluation
dated September 6, 1994. 

No significant hazards consideration comments received: No. 



